name: birdToken
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: $birdToken is a token built on Hashgraph tokenizing our NFT collections and our Token Utility. We bank on our NFTs and a unique Tokenomics to engineer the development and growth of the token. Use cases include Multisender, Token Detective, Portfolio Tracker, P2E and Trading Statistics
